<p align="center">**************Starting With Jobs2Day ******************</p> 




<p align="center" class="NavText">

	Jobs2 Day will help the candidate to search job, <br>
apply for Job and become member of P1acement activlty. It will also<br> 
help the employee to post jobs, upload company profile, select candidate from Job Portal database.<br> 

'Firstly Candidate needs to do reg,istrat\on. In registtat\on 'he has to enter all his information
 like personal details, educational details, experience details and upload resume.<br>
 After the registration process Candidate become member of the Job Portal.<br>
  Candidate can also search for job using different criteria and get result. <br>
  If he wants he can apply for job.Similarly employee also has to do registration first. <br>
In registration he has to enter employee information, requirement details like skills, functional area<br>
 and upload 'company profile. Employee can search candidate and if he finds matching profile for his requirement<br>
  he will call candidate for interview with the help of<br> placement division and placement division <br>
  maintains all interview details and result of each candidate. <br>
In the system candidate can search for job and apply for the jobs but only if they are registered.</p>
